  <brief_title>A Phase 1 Study of MDV3100 in Patients With Castration-Resistant (Hormone-Refractory) Prostate Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 1, Open-label, Dose-escalation Safety And Pharmacokinetic Study Of Mdv3100 In Patients With Castration-resistant Prostate Cancer</official_title>
